text: Ganna Sorokina (; born 31 March 1976 in Zaporizhzhia) is a female diver from Ukraine. ==Career== She won the bronze medal with Olena Zhupina in the Women's 3m Synchronized Springboard competition. Sorokina also competed in the individual 3m Springboard competitions at the 2000 Summer Olympics and the 2004 Summer Olympics.
